---
import { resume } from '../data/resume';
---

<section id="about" class="pt-[clamp(8rem,11vw,12rem)] bg-editorial-surface dark:bg-editorial-surface-dark pb-[clamp(3rem,6vw,5rem)]">
  <div class="w-full px-[clamp(1rem,5vw,7rem)]">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_minmax(0,0.34fr)] items-start lg:items-center gap-[clamp(3rem,6vw,7rem)]">
      
      <!-- Left Column: Text (max-w-3xl) -->
      <div class="space-y-[clamp(2rem,4vw,2.75rem)]">


        <!-- Headline -->
        <h1 class="text-[clamp(3.35rem,7vw,7rem)] font-bold text-editorial-text dark:text-editorial-text-dark tracking-tighter leading-[1.02]" fetchpriority="high">
          Zero to <span class="text-editorial-primary dark:text-editorial-primary-dark">Cloud.</span> <br />
          Done Right.
        </h1>
        
        <!-- Subheading -->
        <p class="text-[clamp(1.25rem,1.5vw,1.625rem)] text-editorial-secondary dark:text-editorial-secondary-dark font-mono font-medium tracking-tight max-w-[68ch] leading-relaxed">
          Production-grade infra. Built from scratch. Delivered on time.
        </p>
 
        <!-- Buttons -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center lg:justify-start gap-4 pt-4">
          <a 
            href="#projects"
            class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 bg-editorial-primary dark:bg-editorial-primary-dark text-white dark:text-editorial-surface-dark font-mono text-[12px] font-bold hover:opacity-90 transition-all text-center"
          >
            View Work
          </a>
          <a 
            href={resume.basics.url || "#"}
            download="Dev_Joshi_Resume.pdf"
            class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 border border-editorial-surface-highest dark:border-editorial-surface-highest-dark bg-white dark:bg-transparent text-editorial-text dark:text-editorial-text-dark font-mono text-[12px] font-bold hover:bg-editorial-surface-low dark:hover:bg-editorial-surface-low-dark transition-all text-center"
          >
            Download CV
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column: Tools List -->
      <div class="hidden lg:flex justify-end">
        <ul class="space-y-12 font-mono text-[15px] font-medium text-[#777] dark:text-editorial-secondary-dark border-l border-[#eee] dark:border-white/5 pl-12 py-4 w-fit">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-[#999] dark:text-editorial-outline"><path d="M17.5 19c.7 0 1.2-.6 1.2-1.3l-.2-6.5c0-.4-.2-.8-.6-1L12.7 7.4c-.4-.2-.9-.2-1.3 0l-5.2 2.8c-.4.2-.6.6-.6 1 l-.2 6.5c0 .7.5 1.3 1.2 1.3h11z"/></svg>
            Amazon Web Services
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-[#999] dark:text-editorial-outline"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"/><path d="M12 2v4"/><path d="M12 18v4"/><path d="M4.93 4.93l2.83 2.83"/><path d="M16.24 16.24l2.83 2.83"/><path d="M2 12h4"/><path d="M18 12h4"/><path d="M4.93 19.07l2.83-2.83"/><path d="M16.24 7.76l2.83-2.83"/></svg>
            Google Cloud Platform
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-[#999] dark:text-editorial-outline"><rect width="7" height="7" x="3" y="3" rx="1"/><rect width="7" height="7" x="14" y="3" rx="1"/><rect width="7" height="7" x="14" y="14" rx="1"/><rect width="7" height="7" x="3" y="14" rx="1"/></svg>
            Kubernetes
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-[#999] dark:text-editorial-outline"><path d="M7 10v4h3v7h4v-7h3l1-4h-4V3h-4v7H7z"/></svg>
            Terraform
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Intro Section (from screenshot bottom) -->
    <div class="mt-[clamp(4rem,7vw,7rem)] pt-10 border-t border-editorial-surface-highest dark:border-editorial-surface-highest-dark grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_minmax(0,0.9fr)] gap-[clamp(3rem,6vw,6rem)]">
      <div class="text-[clamp(1.75rem,2.8vw,2.75rem)] font-bold text-editorial-text dark:text-editorial-text-dark leading-tight tracking-tight">
        Most teams get DevOps half-built. Pipelines that break, infra nobody owns, compliance gaps that surface at the worst time.
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-8 text-[clamp(1.0625rem,1.25vw,1.25rem)] text-editorial-secondary dark:text-editorial-secondary-dark font-light leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          I come in, architect it properly, and ship it. Whether it's a greenfield cloud setup or a high-stakes government migration under compliance deadlines, I've delivered both.
        </p>
        <p>
          Now with AI-augmented tooling (MCP agents, pipeline intelligence) built into my workflow. Not as a buzzword, but as actual open-source tools I've shipped.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
